{"article_id":"2qkpXXKNrD2sxDZS","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump said","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"Saudi Arabia ' s Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman \" totally denied","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"any knowledge \"","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"of what happened","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"when Saudi journalist Jamal Khashoggi went missing this month","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"after visiting the consulate in Istanbul .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"\" Just spoke with the Crown Prince of Saudi Arabia","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"who totally denied","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"any knowledge","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"of what took place in their Turkish Consulate , \"","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"\" He was with Secretary of State Mike Pompeo ...during the call ,","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and told me","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that he has already started ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and will rapidly expand ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"a full and complete investigation into this matter . \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Pompeo met with Saudi Arabian King Salman and the crown prince in Riyadh on Tuesday .","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"In an interview with The Associated Press , Trump compared the situation to the allegations of sexual assault","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"leveled against Supreme Court Justice Brett Kavanaugh during his confirmation hearing .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"`` I think","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"we have to find out what happened first , ''","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"`` Here we go again with ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"you know ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"you 're guilty","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"until proven innocent .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"I do n't like that .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"We just went through that with Justice Kavanaugh","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"and he was innocent all the way","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"as far as I 'm concerned . ''","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"More :","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Trump says","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"rush","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"to condemn Saudi Arabia over Khashoggi","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"is similar to Kavanaugh accusations","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"U.S. resident and Washington Post contributor Khashoggi vanished two weeks ago","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"while visiting the Saudi consulate in Istanbul .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Turkish officials said","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"they have evidence","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"Khashoggi was killed","depth":12},{"id":40,"text":"and dismembered inside the diplomatic compound ,","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"but Saudi officials called the allegations `` baseless . ''","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Pompeo will fly to Ankara on Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"to meet with Turkish officials on the case ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"said Heather Nauert , the State Department 's chief spokeswoman .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Pompeo characterized his meetings with Saudi officials Tuesday as `` direct and candid conversations . '' `` During each of today ' s meetings , the Saudi leadership strongly denied any knowledge","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"of what took place in their consulate in Istanbul , ''","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Pompeo said .","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"`` My assessment from these meetings is that there is serious commitment","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"to determine all the facts","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"and ensure accountability ,","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"including accountability for Saudi Arabia ' s senior leaders or senior officials . ''","depth":13},{"id":52,"text":"Pompeo did not address reports from CNN and The New York Times","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"suggesting","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"the Saudi government would soon release a report","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"that Khashoggi was accidentally killed","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"as a result of a planned rendition back to Saudi Arabia .","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"A spokesman for the Saudi Embassy in Washington did not respond to a request for comment on those reports .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"`` The government of Saudi Arabia owes the Khashoggi family and the world a full and honest explanation of everything","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"that happened to him , ''","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Fred Ryan , publisher and CEO of The Washington Post , said in a statement Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"`` The Saudi government can no longer remain silent ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"and it is essential that our own government and others push harder for the truth . ''","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Ryan supported the Khashoggi 's family request for an independent , international investigation .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Turkish police searched the Saudi consulate in Istanbul overnight Monday","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"and announced Tuesday","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"that the Saudi consul ' s home in Istanbul would be searched .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"A Turkish official told the Associated Press","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that the embassy search revealed information","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"indicating","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"that Khashoggi was killed there .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"In Riyadh , Pompeo held short meetings with Salman and Saudi Foreign Minister Adel al-Jubeir","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"before sitting down with the crown prince , Saudi 's de facto ruler , inside the royal court .","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"\" We are strong and old allies , ''","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"the prince said","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"after greeting Pompeo ,","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"according to a pool report from journalists","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"traveling with the secretary of state .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"`` We face our challenges together","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"- the past , the day of , tomorrow . \"","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Nauert said","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"that during Pompeo 's meeting with the king , the secretary of state thanked Salman for `` his commitment","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"to supporting a thorough , transparent and timely investigation of Jamal Khashoggi ' s disappearance . ''","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"A number of powerful U.S. executives said","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"they pulled out of an investment summit in Riyadh later this month","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"because of the case .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"U.S. Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin plans to attend the conference .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"In Congress , lawmakers in both parties expressed concern about the Saudi government 's alleged involvement in Khashoggi 's disappearance .","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"Some suggested","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"U.S. arms sales to the regime should be halted","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"if it 's determined the journalist was killed inside the consulate .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham , R-S.C. , said","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"the United States should `` sanction the hell out of Saudi Arabia ''","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"and slammed the crown prince ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"known by his initials MBS ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"as a `` toxic '' figure .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"`` This guy is a wrecking ball , ''","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"Graham said on Fox News Tuesday morning ,","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"alleging","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"that the prince directed Khashoggi ' s murder inside the consulate .","depth":15},{"id":100,"text":"`` This guy ' s got ta go . ''","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"Directing his remarks to Saudi Arabian officials ,","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"he said ,","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"`` MBS has tainted your country","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"and tainted himself . ''","depth":14},{"id":105,"text":"Pompeo was dispatched to Saudi Arabia by Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"who warned","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"of `` severe punishment '' for the kingdom","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"if it was involved in Khashoggi ' s disappearance .","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"Trump said Monday","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"that the alleged slaying could have been carried out by `` rogue killers . ''","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"Not only is Saudi Arabia a dominant player in global oil markets ,","depth":4},{"id":112,"text":"it is also a major buyer of U.S. arms","depth":5},{"id":113,"text":"and plays a key role in Washington 's Middle East foreign policy ,","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"aiding anti-terrorism efforts","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"and acting as a reliable bulwark against Iran .","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"More :","depth":2},{"id":117,"text":"Saudis to admit","depth":5},{"id":118,"text":"journalist was killed ,","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"assert death","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"a result of botched interrogation ,","depth":5},{"id":121,"text":"according to media reports","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":243,"left":237,"right":242,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":151,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":138,"right":150,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":138,"left":137,"right":16,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":137,"left":127,"right":136,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":0,"right":126,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":1,"right":125,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":2,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":136,"left":131,"right":135,"relation":"elab